# Casa Petrada E-commerce Website - Cursor Agent Rules

## Project Overview
This is a complete e-commerce website recreation of Casa Petrada (https://casa-petrada.de), a German handmade Boho jewelry and fashion store. The project consists of a modern Vite + TypeScript frontend and a Python FastAPI backend.

## Brand Identity & Design
- **Brand Name**: Casa Petrada
- **Tagline**: "Handgemachter Schmuck & stilvolle Mode" (Handmade jewelry & stylish fashion)
- **Style**: Boho, Natural, Handcrafted, Feminine
- **Colors**: Earth tones, natural colors, warm beiges, soft pinks, blacks
- **Language**: German (primary), with potential for multi-language support

## Product Categories
1. **Armbänder (Bracelets)**
   - Alle Armbänder (All bracelets)
   - Einfacharmbänder (Simple bracelets)
   - Wickelarmbänder (Wrap bracelets)

2. **Ketten (Necklaces)**
   - Alle Ketten (All necklaces)
